name: Digital Bug Resistrider
text:
Cannot be used as material for an Xyz Summon, except for the Xyz Summon of an Insect monster. When you Normal Summon a Level 3 Insect monster: You can Special Summon this card from your hand, then you can make the Levels of both this card and that monster become 5 or 7. If this card is Special Summoned from the hand: You can change the battle position of 1 Insect monster you control. An Xyz Monster that was Summoned using this card on the field as material gains this effect.
? This card gains 1000 ATK/DEF.
